\fs18 \cf4 \cb30 \strokec4 She plunged into an unfathomable abyss.\cb1 \
\cb30 \'97What is this place, and where will it carry her?\cb1 \
\cb30 The moment doubt arose, a voice whispered from the darkness:\cb1 \
\cb30 "This is the realm of the unknown, opening the path to all that is known."\cb1 \
\cb30 Endless shadows tumbled down with her.\cb1 \
\cb30 \'97Who are they, and why do their shadows fall here?\cb1 \
\cb30 As the question rose in her thoughts, the voice replied once more:\cb1 \
\cb30 "They are those cut off from fate. What falls here are the remnants of their past."\cb1 \
\cb30 And so, the little girl hugged herself in solitude, carried downward by countless bygone memories.\cb1 \
\cb30 Her eyes widened in bewilderment, seeing only cold, stillness, and loneliness blooming at the bottom of the abyss.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

