\fs18 \cf4 \cb30 \strokec4 In the darkness lay the girl's slumbering thoughts.\cb1 \
\cb30 They were not innocent daydreams, nor carefree flights of fancy.\cb1 \
\cb30 Her mind was fixed on the memories she had witnessed.\cb1 \
\cb30 "What must I do? What must I bear?"\cb1 \
\cb30 "Good thing it's me, and not someone else."\cb1 \
\cb30 "I know how to deal with being alone... I think."\cb1 \
\cb30 As she sifted through those pasts, the girl calmly accepted this heavy gift.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

