\fs18 \cf4 \cb30 \strokec4 So this is what humanity is \'97 such a complex existence.\cb1 \
\cb30 A lifetime can hold so much joy, and just as much sorrow.\cb1 \
\cb30 Yet now, all of it has fallen into this void, to be swallowed, erased, and buried.\cb1 \
\cb30 No one will ever care again for those joyful laughs, or those grief-stricken cries.\cb1 \
\cb30 Still... every one of those untold stories has been etched into this abyss of the soul.\cb1 \
