\fs18 \cf4 \cb30 \strokec4 "Such beautiful eyes... am I still inside a dream?"\cb1 \
\cb30 It was their first meeting, and her first brush with something real.\cb1 \
\cb30 Amid the emptiness and the grotesque, in the barren abyss that threatened to devour everything, she caught sight of those eyes.\cb1 \
\cb30 They were like a hint of green breaking through the burning desert, like a clear spring rising from a parched riverbed.\cb1 \
\cb30 "I think I've found it... the hope of someone who will willingly respond to me."\cb1 \
